{"tid":308700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[WW3序幕]北韓宣布成功首射洲際導彈 稱可達世界各地","createTime":"2017-07-04T11:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T11:48:19.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef6c14ef099fa9c6a1231f88352dc4065e88ad8","tid":308700,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】北韓國營傳媒發表特別重大報道，宣布首次成功發射洲際彈道導彈。<br />\n<br />\n北韓表示，實踐10年以來的決心，成功發射舞水端14型洲際彈道導，領袖金正恩在現場視察。<br />\n<br />\n北韓指，導彈飛行距離993公里，高度達2802公里，宣稱有能力發射至世界各地。<br />\n<br />\n南韓及美國較早前相信，北韓發射的屬於中遠程導彈，但不排除屬於洲際導彈的可能。南韓總統文在寅主持國家安全保障會議，譴責北韓挑釁，指平壤不負責任，首爾當局不會容忍。<br />\n<br />\n專家指出，北韓的導彈在射程上取得重大進展，或達到超過2800公里的最大高度。相同的導彈在標準彈道下，粗估最大射程可達6700公里；這個射程雖不足打到美國本土或夏威夷，但能涵蓋阿拉斯加州全境。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E9%A6%96%E5%B0%84%E6%B4%B2%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88-%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E9%81%94%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0-071000646.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%258A%259F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%25B0%258E%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%259C%25B0-071000646.html&d=lDLTLuHKMyJrukGQGB7UI0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=0699aa6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E9%A6%96%E5%B0%84%E6%B4%B2%E9%9A%9B%E5%B0%8E%E5%BD%88-%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%AF%E9%81%94%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0-071000646.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/201703200312183_32465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F201703200312183_32465.jpg&h=639d5771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.media.worldjournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/201703200312184_32465.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.media.worldjournal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2F201703200312184_32465.jpg&h=0650fdb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170528/large/28wx01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170528%2Flarge%2F28wx01p.jpg&h=64394a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好買定午餐肉來炒"}]}